data.title: Dell Global Data
data.meta_description: Dell Global Data (1) - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Dell Inc. is an international provider of desktop PCs, software, servers and other IT products. It has four business segments: Large Enterprise, Public, Small and Medium Business, and Consumer. For fiscal year 2012, Dell reported $62.1 billion in revenue with operating profit of $4.4 billion. It offers a variety of products including desktops, laptops, servers, storage and networking equipment, software and peripherals. Dell sells its products through both direct and indirect channels to business and consumer customers worldwide.
